Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:55.91,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:02:01.09,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.....Rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:08.23,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今日が過去に変わる事で、明日が近づいて。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:15.48,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}そんな当たり前の事に　心は傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:19.56,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}あの日見た『世界』を　もう一度作ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:25.05,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}叶う時が　いつか来るなら　もう何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:32.84,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}まるで可能性が無いと　誰に揶揄されても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:37.70,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}次の君に逢える日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:41.65,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繰り返し　巡る運命が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:45.01,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}たとえ　どんな道でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:48.64,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}決して　決して　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:52.41,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}『あした、またね。』　その『未来』を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:56.20,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}いつまでも失くさないように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:59.75,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}終わりのない始まり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:05.13,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}今、君と夢見たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:09.88,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}繋いだ手を　離さないでね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:13.06,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:16.73,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Hope to be with you even after rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:18.94,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm confident we can change.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:08.23,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}用現在覆蓋過去  未來就是這樣步步走近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:15.48,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}如此理所當然  卻依舊心殤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:19.56,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}那天你我所見的『世界』  再一次拼湊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:25.05,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}願望實現之時若能到來  我再無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:32.84,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}即使被人嘲笑不切實際
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:37.70,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}直到再見你為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:45.01,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}縱使顛沛輪迴的命運再艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:48.64,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我也絕對  絕對  不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:52.41,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}『明天再見』  那一份『未來』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:56.20,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}讓我們一直珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:59.75,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}一旦開始  再無休止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:05.13,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}現在我只願和你一起  去瞭望夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:09.88,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}緊握的雙手  不會再分離
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:16.08,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心では何度も　好きと伝えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:26.55,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想いは残るの？　わたし消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:36.56,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君の声　真っ直ぐな瞳　忘れない温もり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:45.29,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}記憶の中に閉じ込めたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:51.60,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}変えられないこと　変えてしまいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:23:01.85,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}何度でも運命の中を　笑いあって　ふざけあって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:07.63,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}「明日また会えるよね」　きっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:18.71,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}会いたい　ただひとつだけ願い叶うなら
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:16.08,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在心中曾千百次  向你表述過愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:26.55,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}是否會留下情思  即便我終會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:36.56,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你的聲響  直視的目光  是無法忘懷的暖陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:45.29,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想要烙刻在記憶上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:51.60,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}無從改變之物  卻又想要改變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:23:01.85,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不斷在輪迴命運中  一同嬉笑  一同玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:07.63,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一定能夠「明天再會」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:18.71,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}願與你相會  若這唯一的祈願將能實現
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是啊  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能想起些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家裡的事情啊學校裡的事情之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觸碰盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觸碰  盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盒子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說一股犯罪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了哦  進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸虧愛理還有多出來的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為了這樣的非常時刻而備著的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是為了暴走的時候而準備的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh it suits you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被盯著看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  結同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.07,0:01:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  我們很久以前開始就一直在研究這個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你熱點牛奶  好讓你好好睡一覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觸碰  盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今為止的一切
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:25.87,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(603,302)}『剩下的時間』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後我重複了多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結  要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  現在什麼都別問…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等等  結
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  腳上的傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不礙事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得找人來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織同學  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是想回避事故  結局就會變得越悲慘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像是在警告我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏…秋…秋山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早就開始翹課嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想曬曬太陽就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像上了年紀的人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  好想向你求助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就向你坦白一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛  哎  不過話說回來真的好想翹課啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長眠不起的人？是計程車司機來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可怕了  咱們學校好像也有好幾個人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川同學知道剛才說的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  聽說過一些傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「內濱綜合症」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在內濱周邊頻繁發生的謎一樣的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無預兆的  人們突然陷入長眠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣再也不會醒來  謎一樣的病症
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著騷動還沒有擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊  居然要我們調查幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺有趣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不有趣啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}「幽靈」？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}就是Ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽靈的真身就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}總之明天先開始找人取證  然後再實地調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}好麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我覺得…我待在這裡就好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準確的說是由於不斷穿越回同一段時間而產生的我的殘像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\q2}是其他時間線上的我重合起來  受到量子振動的影響而產生的投影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不行的嘛  佳織也一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又引發了其他嚴重的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在某個時間線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到啊  真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼情況  影像？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我的影子接觸的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時間線的東八重子  據我所知再也沒有醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推測下來恐怕是因為量子振動的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有意識被拉入其他時間線去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說附近又出現了  「內濱綜合症」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕啊  至少能知道發病原因也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是幽靈幹的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}等…等等奏  別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「內濱綜合症」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有以下三種情況  會讓人容易受到量子振動的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接接觸到我的影子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然波長一致的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有就是  對我想要改變未來這件事進行干涉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人發病的概率都會增加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  就來決定一下幽靈調查小組的分組吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}去抓Japanese ghost吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是幽靈還是內濱綜合症
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著我進行時間跳躍的次數增加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生的頻率會越來越高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這裡的成員中的某一個因此陷入沉睡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間就會喪失連續性  在未來我就不會被製作出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的存在本身就會消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話  佳織同學也就無法回避事故…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我是和誰一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓奏能帶上笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是和秋山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就和佳織一組了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說這裡是報告目擊到幽靈最多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他還有東西突然墜落  窗戶玻璃振動之類的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來沒什麼東西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我被傳送回來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是還殘留著量子振動的影響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川害怕幽靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不怎麼怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是呢  都這麼大了居然還會怕幽靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受傷了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才你直接叫我名字了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  不好意思  一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來最開始相遇的時候你也是叫我奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}什麼聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  鬧得真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化節的準備也很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就剩委託給我們的幽靈調查了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支倉同學快來  柔道部和空手道部…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受了傷的話  佳織就可以躲過受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經是在其他的時間線上驗證過了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  對不起  結
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  佐佐木同學沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  這之後就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所抗衡的時間的修正  因果的鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的力量十分強大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會之後再說明理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請暫時在這裡待一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.89,0:10:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結  哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是限制佳織自身的行動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會引發完全無法預料的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對現實的的介入不得不謹慎進行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不以最小的介入對事故進行回避的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼是可以的  什麼又是不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷地重複  得出了答案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  這次肯定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不那麼痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼幽靈事件也就告一段落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\q2}真是的  柔道部也是  電影研究學會也是  都不幹點正事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Japanese ghost  明明好想見一面的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷增多的我的影子  內濱症候群
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天我進行時間逆行這件事本身都會受到阻撓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前  不救出佳織同學的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也為了奏的笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了古川  還在疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我救下佳織同學  未來就會因此改變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話  我的存在本身又…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我就是為了這個才在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對結怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  你問怎麼看…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}這個Symptom的意思是前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}Boldness是勇敢的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}真愛來臨的前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}對男性來說就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什  什…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你突然問我這個我也答不上來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡結嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和古川也才剛認識不久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你為什麼要問這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  只是問問而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那個時候我沒能明確地否定自己喜歡古川
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底…是怎麼想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織請假了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好像身體不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不舒服？  怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到現在為止都沒發生過這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找佳織有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因呢！？  你有什麼線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這也不能算是原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  古川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相機怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！？  奏！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川  你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去佳織同學家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天佳織同學不可能請假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是有什麼理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織同學請假的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織不來難道會有什麼麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我們都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文學會的一員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天一定會把佳織帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止我一個人  大家也都很擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我順路買些什麼東西帶回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個  那就  布丁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒事了  告訴大家明天我會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思讓大家為我擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結  腳沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  已經好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為你又和奏吵架了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起用這個相機拍張照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  突然之間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正好也想試試傳統相機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那機會難得  乾脆就在外面拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  這才是天文學會的感覺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:15:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那下拍好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這樣的時間能一直延續下去就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話想和你說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給  給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓開讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支倉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳…  不  佐佐木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我佳織就好了  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才想對我說什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  其實呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  真是的  有凪沙學姐在真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是小小的玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是天文學會成員的徽章
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然遲了點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼開心事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為身為古川迷的我感受到你渾身上下散發出的歡快的氣氛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花梨  來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生的事大都不會變化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我以為只不過是和以前一樣的  時間的延長而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  結  餅乾烤好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支倉同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把烤好的餅乾送給那兩個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…結
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結  你對奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能聽到你的心裡話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  對秋山同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前問過奏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問他對結怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然奏沒有明確回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我認為他應該是喜歡結的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:18:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…也很喜歡奏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從以前就一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也曾經有一次想要放棄過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我無法對自己撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟我還是喜歡著奏的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  忽然說這種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  要是那樣我到底又是為什麼才來到這裡的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  結
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古川！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和佳織之間發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請回應她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請回應佳織同學的感情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什  什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是你最…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡誰是我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是喜歡佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是愛理  凪沙學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結  你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我馬上就會消失不見的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失不見是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要轉學去其他地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在無法說明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我能停留在這裡的時間只剩下一點點了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請一定要對佳織…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你將
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你將無法得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽不懂啊
